# Testing and Regression

- Every bug fix should include a reproducible check.
- Add focused tests for core rules (damage, death, cooldown, state transitions).
- Prefer deterministic test inputs; avoid random behavior in tests.
- Keep test names behavior-based (`Should_X_When_Y`).

# Regression Checklist

- Can start a run, fail, and restart without soft lock.
- Core combat actions still work after refactors.
- Save/config load does not crash with previous data.

# Example

```csharp
[Test]
public void Should_Die_When_UnmitigatedHitReceived() { /* ... */ }
```
